Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:01.01,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:44.83,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:50.50,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:56.05,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:59.77,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,从远方传来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.34,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,心为之而动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:05.71,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:13.28,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,这悲伤的预感将是否成真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:19.19,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,未曾知晓的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:26.39,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:32.61,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:38.55,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,梦中迷惘 而充满自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:44.20,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,轻声许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:49.61,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,好想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.59,0:23:57.28,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:01.01,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.66,0:24:12.12,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:16.17,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也许和真澄合二为一之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:19.09,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才能更多得陪在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:22.36,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真响
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:26.83,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲 你快过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.18,0:24:29.72,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真夏要被真澄带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.34,0:24:36.36,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想成为普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:37.86,cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
